<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="th">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Dashboard - เวชระเบียน</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/static/style.css">
</head>
<body onload="authGuard(); loadPatients()">
    <div class="wrapper">
        <nav class="sidebar">
            <div class="sidebar-header">
                <h3>รพ.ดอกคำใต้</h3>
                <p>Medical Record System</p>
            </div>
            <ul class="menu">
                <li><a href="/dashboard" class="active">
                    <svg class="icon-svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M10 20v-6h4v6h5v-8h3L12 3 2 12h3v8z"/></svg>
                    ภาพรวม
                </a></li>
                <li><a href="/register">
                    <svg class="icon-svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M15 12c2.21 0 4-1.79 4-4s-1.79-4-4-4-4 1.79-4 4 1.79 4 4 4zm-9-2V7H4v3H1v2h3v3h2v-3h3v-2H6zm9 4c-2.67 0-8 1.34-8 4v2h16v-2c0-2.66-5.33-4-8-4z"/></svg>
                    ลงทะเบียนผู้ป่วยใหม่
                </a></li>
                <li><a href="/patient-list">
                    <svg class="icon-svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M16 11c1.66 0 2.99-1.34 2.99-3S17.66 5 16 5c-1.66 0-3 1.34-3 3s1.34 3 3 3zm-8 0c1.66 0 2.99-1.34 2.99-3S9.66 5 8 5C6.34 5 5 6.34 5 8s1.34 3 3 3zm0 2c-2.33 0-7 1.17-7 3.5V19h14v-2.5c0-2.33-4.67-3.5-7-3.5zm8 0c-.29 0-.62.02-.97.05 1.16.84 1.97 1.97 1.97 3.45V19h6v-2.5c0-2.33-4.67-3.5-7-3.5z"/></svg>
                    ฐานข้อมูลผู้ป่วย
                </a></li>
                <li><a href="#" onclick="logout()">
                    <svg class="icon-svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M10.09 15.59L11.5 17l5-5-5-5-1.41 1.41L12.67 11H3v2h9.67l-2.58 2.59zM19 3H5c-1.11 0-2 .9-2 2v4h2V5h14v14H5v-4H3v4c0 1.1.89 2 2 2h14c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V5c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2z"/></svg>
                    ออกจากระบบ
                </a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>

        <div class="main-content">
            <div class="header-title">ภาพรวมระบบ (Dashboard)</div>
            <div class="stats-grid">
                <div class="card">
                    <div>
                        <h4>ผู้ป่วยทั้งหมด</h4>
                        <span id="totalCount"><%= totalPatients %></span> คน
                    </div>
                    <svg class="card-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M16 11c1.66 0 2.99-1.34 2.99-3S17.66 5 16 5c-1.66 0-3 1.34-3 3s1.34 3 3 3zm-8 0c1.66 0 2.99-1.34 2.99-3S9.66 5 8 5C6.34 5 5 6.34 5 8s1.34 3 3 3zm0 2c-2.33 0-7 1.17-7 3.5V19h14v-2.5c0-2.33-4.67-3.5-7-3.5zm8 0c-.29 0-.62.02-.97.05 1.16.84 1.97 1.97 1.97 3.45V19h6v-2.5c0-2.33-4.67-3.5-7-3.5z"/></svg>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <div>
                        <h4>แพทย์ออกตรวจ</h4>
                        <span>5</span> ท่าน
                    </div>
                    <svg class="card-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M6 22h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8l-6-6-6 6v12a2 2 0 0 0 2 2zm7-11h-4v-2h4v-2h2v2h4v2h-4v2h-2v-2z" transform="scale(0.8) translate(3,3)"/></svg>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <script src="/static/script.js"></script>
</body>
</body>
</html>